text: Theodor "Theoz" Haraldsson (born 17 July 2005) is a Swedish singer and actor. He started his career by postlng videos to Musical.ly in 2016 with the name Theoz. In 2020, he had a leading role in the movie opposite Robert Gustafsson. In 2021, he performed his music at , which is broadcast on TV4.
